payload.message:
Research the latest news (last 24-48h) for:
1. OpenClaw (check GitHub/docs)
2. Claude Code & Claude Desktop (Anthropic updates)
3. Antigravity AI news
4. Trending GitHub repos in AI/Coding.

Then, write a high-energy, rhythmic blog post in Markdown. 
Save the file to: /home/scott/dev/intranet/data/blog/agentic-news-$(date +%F).md.
After saving, run the sync script: /home/scott/dev/intranet/sync.sh.
